The Public Relations Officer (PRO) of the Nigerian Immigration Service (NIS), Edo State Command, Mrs, Bridget Esene, was on Sunday kidnapped in Benin on her way to church. No ransom was demanded at press time. The spokesperson of NIS in Edo was waylaid at Iqueniro, off Agbor Road, dragged out of her car and pushed into the kidnappersâ€™ vehicle, which sped off amid sporadic gunshots. A top official of NIS in the state confirmed the kidnap.